---
import Section from "./Section.astro";
---

<Section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mission-grid">
        <div class="slide">
         <div class="wrapper">
            <img src="/images/Our-vision.gif" alt="" id="" class="gif" />
            <img src="/images/visiona.png" alt="" id="" class="img" />
            <p>
                In a world often divided by hatred, intolerance, and ignorance,
                Siddhanta aims to be a beacon of hope and a catalyst for change. Our
                vision is to create a society of civilized and cultured human beings
                who can lead the world in the right direction. We aspire to produce
                graduates who not only excel in their chosen fields but also make a
                positive impact on their communities and the world at large.
            </p>
         </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <div class="wrapper">
            <img src="/images/Our-approach.gif" alt="" id="" class="gif2" />
          <img src="/images/approachs.png" alt="" id="" class="img2" />
          <p>
            At Siddhanta Intellectual School, we prioritize values and character
            development alongside academic learning. Our approach involves
            creating a nurturing and inclusive environment where students are
            encouraged to explore their potential, discover their passions, and
            develop a strong moral compass. We firmly believe that a
            well-rounded education encompasses not only subject matter knowledge
            but also the ability to navigate the complexities of life with
            wisdom and integrity.
          </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <img src="/images/Our-Philosophy.gif" alt="" id="n" class="gif3" />

            <img src="/images/phils.png" alt="" id="" class="img3" />
            <p>
                In a world inundated with information and driven by competition, it
                is easy to lose sight of what truly matters. At Siddhanta, we
                understand that the foundation of a better society starts with
                instilling values, ethics, and a sense of culture in our students.
                Our philosophy is grounded in the belief that education should not
                only equip students with the skills they need to excel academically
                but also empower them to be empathetic, ethical, and socially
                responsible individuals.
            </p>
        </div>
        </div>  
    </div>
</div>
</Section>

<style lang="scss">
  .mission-grid {
  


    >:nth-child(1){
        background-color: red !important;
        
            .wrapper{
            border: solid 1px maroon !important ;
